import React from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'antd'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Navigation = () => {
  return (
    <Menu mode='horizontal'>
      <Menu.Item>
        <Link to="/">首页</Link>
      </Menu.Item>
      <Menu.Item>
        <Link to="/shop">商场</Link>
      </Menu.Item>
    </Menu>
  )
}

export default Navigation
